					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7291988#post-3948190</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7291988/grin-and-bear-it#post-3948190</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 01 Sep 2018 07:05:08 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>keyii</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4420424</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This was written for OCT2018 &#8212; thank you so much to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1553042&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536033272" alt="PeppersGhost" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1553042)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" >PeppersGhost</a></span> for organising it! I was really glad for the opportunity to write my first ever tale.</p> <p>Special thanks:</p> <ul> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/eskobar" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1173523&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536033272" alt="Eskobar" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1173523)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/eskobar" >Eskobar</a></span>, patron saint of stepfathers and master of helpful critique. You are amazing. This would literally not exist without you. Thank you so so much for taking time out of your busy busy schedule to help me.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=414239&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536033272" alt="Gabriel Jade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=414239)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" >Gabriel Jade</a></span> and the majestic <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sir-baubius" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2200357&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536033272" alt="Sir Baubius" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2200357)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sir-baubius" >Sir Baubius</a></span> for looking kindly this over.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tsatpwtcotttadc" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3681296&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536033272" alt="TSATPWTCOTTTADC" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3681296)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tsatpwtcotttadc" >TSATPWTCOTTTADC</a></span> for catching most of my truly ridiculous number of typos (hence the revision history), for helping me with the original Snapchat screenshots, and for formatting help.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/newyrose" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4354260&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536033272" alt="NewyRose" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4354260)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/newyrose" >NewyRose</a></span> for her incredible CSS work in imitating the Snapchat interface! She is a CSS goddess. We should all worship her.</li> </ul> <p>Regardless of how OCT goes, this will probably be the start of a series meant to characterise 3009 and its relationship with 3009-C. Stay tuned!</p> <p>And I'll take this opportunity to link both of Maya's articles: here's <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/maya-the-magnificent">her Herman Fuller tale</a> by my lovely opponent <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/secretcrow" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3604422&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536033272" alt="SecretCrow" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3604422)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/secretcrow" >SecretCrow</a></span> and <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/critter-profile-maya">the Wilson's Wildlife Solutions write-up</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536033272" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span>, who I adore. Thanks for creating this amazing character!</p> <p>(EDIT: I'm so sorry for forgetting to credit you, Baubs!! Oops.)</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
